{
 "name": "RPlog_Meet_Brek",
 "title": "Meet Brek",
 "summary": "On a crowded city street, the newly arrived gunman Brek Halsmer crosses paths with the medic Myiari and Senator Tokoga, fresh back from troubles on Delar, along with the pilot Lanze who keeps getting jostled by the crowd. Their reunion is shattered when an armored Mandalorian-liveried assailant, apparently the same faction that broke the criminal Nass out of jail, opens fire and targets the Senator. Brek, Myiari, and Tokoga scatter and return fire in a running street battle, but the attacker overpowers Tokoga and presses a blade to his throat before fleeing, leaving the Senator shaken but alive. In the aftermath the three trade rueful stories of their disastrous first days, and Brek introduces himself properly to Myiari, the grim gunman managing a rare warm smile.",
